query:
SELECT 
  pw.id,
  pw.waveNumber,
  pw.status as wave_status,
  pw.pickedBy,
  pw.pickedAt,
  po.id as order_id,
  po.orderNumber,
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  po.status as order_status,
  po.pickedBy as order_pickedBy,
  po.pickedAt as order_pickedAt
FROM pickingWaves pw
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pw.id = po.waveId
WHERE pw.waveNumber = 'OS-20260121-0001'
ORDER BY po.id;
